Requires

   Linux
   Linux overlayfs in Kernel (3.18+; 2014)
   Linux LSB base
   Standard POSIX /bin/sh
   Standard GNU command line programs
   rsync

To install the program for system wide use:

   sh makefile.sh help
   sh makefile.sh install

To run run "in place" for easy "git pull" updates:

   sh makefile.sh install-symlink
